      "northStar": "Nocturnal Data Canvas — a dark, subdued interface punctuated by bursts of algorithmic color.",
      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"\n  --color-midnight-base: #0c0c0c;\n  --color-charcoal-surface: #25262d;\n  --color-slate-accent: #383a42;\n  --color-ghost-text: #f2f2f3;\n  --color-cool-gray-text: #858893;\n  --color-subtle-gray-text: #54565f;\n  --color-indigo-button: #384270;\n  --font-replica-regular: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-replica-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-arial: Arial, sans-serif;\n  background: var(--color-midnight-base);\n  padding: 32px 24px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  width: 600px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n\">\n  <!-- Active/Open button -->\n  <button style=\"\n    background: var(--color-indigo-button);\n    color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n    font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n    line-height: 1.0;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 24px;\n    padding: 14px 24px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  \">\n    <span style=\"\n      width: 10px;\n      height: 10px;\n      background: #6ee86e;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: inline-block;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    \"></span>\n    Open\n  </button>\n\n  <!-- Get in touch pill button -->\n  <button style=\"\n    background: var(--color-slate-accent);\n    color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n    font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n    line-height: 1.0;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 64px;\n    padding: 14px 24px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  \">\n    Get in touch →\n  </button>\n\n  <!-- Start a project pill button -->\n  <button style=\"\n    background: var(--color-slate-accent);\n    color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n    font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n    line-height: 1.0;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 64px;\n    padding: 14px 24px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  \">\n    Start a project →\n  </button>\n</div>",
          "name": "CTA Button Group",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"\n  --color-midnight-base: #0c0c0c;\n  --color-charcoal-surface: #25262d;\n  --color-slate-accent: #383a42;\n  --color-ghost-text: #f2f2f3;\n  --color-cool-gray-text: #858893;\n  --color-subtle-gray-text: #54565f;\n  --color-indigo-button: #384270;\n  --font-replica-regular: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-replica-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-arial: Arial, sans-serif;\n  background: var(--color-midnight-base);\n  padding: 24px;\n  width: 600px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n\">\n  <!-- Year label -->\n  <div style=\"\n    font-family: var(--font-replica-mono);\n    font-size: 20px;\n    color: var(--color-subtle-gray-text);\n    letter-spacing: normal;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  \">2023</div>\n\n  <!-- Card body -->\n  <div style=\"\n    background: var(--color-charcoal-surface);\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    padding: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  \">\n    <!-- Image placeholder -->\n    <div style=\"\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 200px;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a2a 0%, #0f1f3a 40%, #2a1a3a 100%);\n      border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n    \">\n      <div style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: var(--color-subtle-gray-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n      \">Metadrop — App Preview</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Content row -->\n    <div style=\"\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr 170px;\n      gap: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    \">\n      <!-- Project name -->\n      <div style=\"\n        padding: 16px 12px;\n        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n      \">\n        <div style=\"\n          font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n          font-size: 20px;\n          color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n          letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n          line-height: 1.2;\n          font-weight: 400;\n        \">Metadrop</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Description -->\n      <div style=\"\n        padding: 16px 12px;\n        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n        border-left: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n      \">\n        <p style=\"\n          font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n          font-size: 13px;\n          color: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n          letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n          line-height: 1.5;\n          margin: 0;\n        \">I've lead design at Metadrop, a project for launching and discovering Coins & NFT drops. There I designed all products and their landing pages, apps to build fully custom drops and consumer interfaces to mint, explore and trade.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Tags -->\n      <div style=\"\n        padding: 16px 12px;\n        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n        border-left: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 6px;\n      \">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cool-gray-text); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;\"></div>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-replica-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-cool-gray-text); line-height: 1.2;\">Art Direction</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cool-gray-text); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;\"></div>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-replica-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-cool-gray-text); line-height: 1.2;\">Branding</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cool-gray-text); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;\"></div>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-replica-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-cool-gray-text); line-height: 1.2;\">Design Systems</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cool-gray-text); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;\"></div>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-replica-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-cool-gray-text); line-height: 1.2;\">Product Design</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Footer links -->\n    <div style=\"\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 0;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n    \">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        padding: 12px 16px;\n        border-right: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n        display: inline-block;\n      \">Homepage →</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        padding: 12px 16px;\n        display: inline-block;\n      \">App →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Project Card — Metadrop",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"\n  --color-midnight-base: #0c0c0c;\n  --color-charcoal-surface: #25262d;\n  --color-slate-accent: #383a42;\n  --color-ghost-text: #f2f2f3;\n  --color-cool-gray-text: #858893;\n  --color-subtle-gray-text: #54565f;\n  --color-indigo-button: #384270;\n  --font-replica-regular: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-replica-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;\n  --font-arial: Arial, sans-serif;\n  background: var(--color-midnight-base);\n  width: 600px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n\">\n  <!-- Name row -->\n  <div style=\"\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: baseline;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n  \">\n    <span style=\"\n      font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n      font-size: 20px;\n      color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n      letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n      line-height: 1.0;\n    \">Maciej</span>\n    <span style=\"\n      font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n      letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n      line-height: 1.2;\n    \">pronounced 'much-yay'</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Bio content -->\n  <div style=\"\n    background: var(--color-charcoal-surface);\n    padding: 28px 20px 32px;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 32px;\n  \">\n    <!-- First paragraph -->\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 20px;\n        color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n        margin: 0;\n      \">I'm a design generalist and my work spans across multiple disciplines from product design to branding, engineering and art. I went down the design rabbit hole doing things on the internet like flash websites and Mac themes and after graduating in graphic design in 2010 I started my own studio.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Second paragraph -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-end;\">\n      <p style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 20px;\n        color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n        margin: 0;\n      \">Since then I've been lucky to work with brands big and small, teams of two and companies of thousands, on projects that spanned the many disciplines of contemporary design.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Hello intro band -->\n  <div style=\"\n    background: var(--color-midnight-base);\n    padding: 20px;\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-slate-accent);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 16px;\n  \">\n    <div style=\"\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    \">\n      <div style=\"\n        width: 18px;\n        height: 18px;\n        border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n      \">\n        <div style=\"\n          width: 8px;\n          height: 8px;\n          background: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n          border-radius: 50%;\n        \"></div>\n      </div>\n      <span style=\"\n        font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n        font-size: 20px;\n        color: var(--color-cool-gray-text);\n        letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n        line-height: 1.0;\n      \">Hello</span>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"\n      font-family: var(--font-replica-regular);\n      font-size: 20px;\n      color: var(--color-ghost-text);\n      letter-spacing: -0.014em;\n      line-height: 1.4;\n      margin: 0;\n    \">I'm Maciej and I'm an independent designer. I help ambitious founders and companies in building their vision, brands and products.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "About Bio Block",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
